    "Feedback is a crucial element in the evaluation of essay writing.",
    "Merely assigning grades to essays does not effectively aid students in enhancing their essay writing abilities.",
    "In addition to scoring, guiding students on areas for improvement and how to enhance their writing skills is pivotal in the learning process of essay writing (Patchan et al. 2016).",
    "Several studies focus on the generation of feedback in automated essay scoring by identifying the most crucial aspects of the essay that influenced the assigned score.",
